      "Eumpe begins in Brussels and Sabena His there every day.\nSABENA\nFunny,\nyou don't look Belgian.\ncompletely comfortable. And that goes for economy class as\nPlenty of genuine old-world Belgian courtesyand service,\ntoo. Including the services of stewards and stewardesses who\nknow about everything from selecting wines to making vou\ncall Sabena.\nEurope begins in Brussels and Sabena flies there every day."
